name: std::sync::mpmc::context::Context::try_select
src:
pub fn try_select(&self, select: Selected) -> Result<(), Selected> {
        self.inner
            .select
            .compare_exchange(
                Selected::Waiting.into(),
                select.into(),
                Ordering::AcqRel,
                Ordering::Acquire,
            )
            .map(|_| ())
            .map_err(|e| e.into())
    }
